<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Wikiful</title>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>

  <!--[if lt IE 9]>
      <script src="http://html5shim.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/html5.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <![endif]-->
</head>
<body>

 <nav class="navbar navbar-default" role="navigation">
 	<div class="container-fluid">
 		<div class="navbar-header">
 			<%= link_to "Wikiful", root_path, :class => "navbar-brand" %>
   		</div>
		<ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right">
        	<li class='session-controls'> 
            <% if current_user %>
            <%= link_to "Log Out", logout_path, :class => 'btn btn-primary' %>
              Logged in as <%= current_user.email %>.
            <% else %>
            <div class="btn-group">
              <%= link_to "Sign Up", signup_path, :class => "btn btn-default" %>
              <%= link_to "Log In", login_path, :class => "btn btn-default" %>
            </div>
            <% end %>
         </li>
        </ul>
   	</div>
</nav>

<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <% flash.each do |name, msg| %>
        <%= content_tag :div, msg, id: "flash_#{name}" %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-9"><%= yield %></div> 
      <div class="col-md-3 sidebar">
      
          <div class="panel panel-default">
              <div class="panel-heading">
                <h3 class="panel-title">My Wikiful</h3>
              </div>
          <div class="panel-body">
  
            <%= link_to "Write a Wiki", new_article_path, :class => 'btn btn-primary' %>
           
          
              <h4>Categories</h4>
              <ul>
                <% @categories.each do |category| %>
                  <li><%= link_to category.title, category %></li>
                <% end %>
              </ul>
            
            <div class="about">
              <h4>About Wikiful</h4>
              <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Accusantium architecto earum neque perspiciatis quia animi debitis quod repellat vitae explicabo. Sapiente aliquam reprehenderit id vitae atque ducimus facere molestias soluta?</p>
            </div>
          </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
